rules.ruleString: (Must have passed 1 (I/W) units in {OCC3062, OCC3072} AND  Must have passed 1 (I/W) units in {OCC4081})
Must be enrolled in course version {3869, M3001}

description: This unit will enable students to consider their own role within health and human service organisations, and apply and critique contemporary practice knowledge in areas such as leadership and management, team functioning and governance.The Unit will conclude with a conference that includes presentations of research and project work from occupational therapy and physiotherapy students.Students will complete a range of on-line tasks while completing their fieldwork placement as part of the unit OCC4082
faculty: Faculty of Medicine, Nursing and Health Sciences
